{"tid":713819,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"施蒙尼：阿根廷沒有領袖","createTime":"2018-06-23T06:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T07:58:48.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7a55ba7b22b8677d68aa4e07b7af82dd54cc90ca","tid":713819,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:52:09.000Z","msg":"美斯還是C朗拿度更加好？施蒙尼認為C朗在普通球隊都可以有發揮，但美斯一定要出色的球員輔助，現在阿根廷是沒有領袖。<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷以0：3不敵克羅地亞，美斯賽後受到千夫所指。施蒙尼指出美斯及C朗拿度的不同，美斯一定要有好球員幫助，相反C朗在普通球隊都可以有所發揮。<br />\n<br />\n「阿根廷最大問題是沒有領袖，無論是足總還是教練也好。我完全見不到有人領導球隊，教練也好、球員也好，現在的阿根廷完全迷失了。」施蒙尼說。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=MmEE7c2Km%2FnVFkRvx4LWIVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=4cba49ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"50fcd99e4ab67d7187293fb07e63d414c8e1096e","tid":713819,"uid":10733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"要救國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73bd35526ac1fc925b347e2fdd65a3d782882bb","tid":713819,"uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:20:42.000Z","msg":"佢個仔幾時可以取代agger路條廢閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe3971003dc7d2e12da422e3901caba613f79f4","tid":713819,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:26:20.000Z","msg":"明明係C朗等比人餵 施蒙尼係咪唔識波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747bd1e6314fca3717198e7b966df0bc2bf78a21","tid":713819,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:54:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09cb695753a3586693842612a9b98d4830db2415","tid":713819,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"747bd1e6314fca3717198e7b966df0bc2bf78a21","tid":7